
1. Core Table

DimCompany

CompanyId INT IDENTITY PK

CompanyCode VARCHAR(50)

CompanyName NVARCHAR(255)

TradeName NVARCHAR(255)

DateOfIncorporation DATE

CountryCode VARCHAR(10)

LegalStructure NVARCHAR(100)

RegisteredAddressId INT FK → DimAddress

OperationalAddressId INT FK → DimAddress

BusinessLicenseNumber NVARCHAR(50)

LicenseExpiryDate DATE

OfficialPhone NVARCHAR(50)

OfficialEmail NVARCHAR(255)

Website NVARCHAR(255)

CreatedAt DATETIME

UpdatedAt DATETIME

2. Address Table

DimAddress

AddressId INT IDENTITY PK

AddressLine NVARCHAR(500)

City NVARCHAR(100)

Country NVARCHAR(100)

POBox NVARCHAR(50)

PostalCode NVARCHAR(20)

3. Shareholders

FactCompanyShareholders

ShareholderId INT IDENTITY PK

CompanyId INT FK → DimCompany

ShareholderName NVARCHAR(255)

Nationality NVARCHAR(100)

Percentage DECIMAL(5,2)

IsUBO BIT

UBOId NVARCHAR(100)

4. Management

FactCompanyManagement

ManagementId INT IDENTITY PK

CompanyId INT FK → DimCompany

PersonName NVARCHAR(255)

Role NVARCHAR(100)

IsAuthorizedSignatory BIT

5. Business Activities

FactCompanyActivities

ActivityId INT IDENTITY PK

CompanyId INT FK → DimCompany

ActivityName NVARCHAR(255)

ActivityCode NVARCHAR(50)

IsFreeZoneQualifying BIT

6. Financials

DimCompanyFinancials

FinancialId INT IDENTITY PK

CompanyId INT UNIQUE FK → DimCompany

FiscalYearEnd TINYINT

AccountingStandards NVARCHAR(50)

ExternalAuditor NVARCHAR(255)

7. Banking

FactCompanyBanking

BankId INT IDENTITY PK

CompanyId INT FK → DimCompany

BankName NVARCHAR(255)

AccountNumber NVARCHAR(100)

Currency NVARCHAR(10)

LoanDetails NVARCHAR(MAX)

OverdraftLimit DECIMAL(18,2)

8. Tax & Compliance

DimCompanyTax

TaxId INT IDENTITY PK

CompanyId INT UNIQUE FK → DimCompany

VATRegNo NVARCHAR(50)

VATDate DATE

CorporateTaxRegNo NVARCHAR(50)

CorporateTaxDate DATE

FreeZoneBenefit NVARCHAR(255)

Exemptions NVARCHAR(MAX)

9. Group Structure

FactCompanyGroup

GroupId INT IDENTITY PK

CompanyId INT FK → DimCompany

RelatedEntityName NVARCHAR(255)

RelationType NVARCHAR(50)

Country NVARCHAR(100)

OwnershipPercentage DECIMAL(5,2)

10. Contracts

FactCompanyContracts

ContractId INT IDENTITY PK

CompanyId INT FK → DimCompany

ContractType NVARCHAR(100)

PartyName NVARCHAR(255)

ContractValue DECIMAL(18,2)

ExpiryDate DATE

Notes NVARCHAR(MAX)

11. HR

DimCompanyHR

HRId INT IDENTITY PK

CompanyId INT UNIQUE FK → DimCompany

TotalEmployees INT

WPSNumber NVARCHAR(50)

Policies NVARCHAR(MAX)

12. Insurance

FactCompanyInsurance

InsuranceId INT IDENTITY PK

CompanyId INT FK → DimCompany

InsuranceType NVARCHAR(100)

Provider NVARCHAR(255)

CoverageAmount DECIMAL(18,2)

ExpiryDate DATE

13. IT

DimCompanyIT

ITId INT IDENTITY PK

CompanyId INT UNIQUE FK → DimCompany

ERPSystem NVARCHAR(100)

CybersecurityPolicy NVARCHAR(MAX)

BackupRecoveryPlan NVARCHAR(MAX)
